{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-437-fibonacci-primitive-roots","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 437: Prirodni koreni Fibonaccija","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Kada izračunamo $8^n$ modulo 11 za $n = 0$ do 9, dobijamo: 1, 8, 9, 6, 4, 10, 3, 2, 5, 7.</p>\n<p>Kako vidimo, sve moguće vrednosti od 1 do 10 su vidljive. Stoga, 8 je prirodni koren 11.</p>\n<p>Ali postoji još:</p>\n<p>Ako pažljivo pogledamo, vidimo:</p>\n<p>$$\\begin{align}\n&#x26; 1 + 8 = 9 \\\\\n&#x26; 8 + 9 = 17 ≡ 6\\bmod 11 \\\\\n&#x26; 9 + 6 = 15 ≡ 4\\bmod 11 \\\\\n&#x26; 6 + 4 = 10 \\\\\n&#x26; 4 + 10 = 14 ≡ 3\\bmod 11 \\\\\n&#x26; 10 + 3 = 13 ≡ 2\\bmod 11 \\\\\n&#x26; 3 + 2 = 5 \\\\\n&#x26; 2 + 5 = 7 \\\\\n&#x26; 5 + 7 = 12 ≡ 1\\bmod 11.\n\\end{align}$$</p>\n<p>Moć 8 mod 11 ima ciklus i period od 10, i $8^n + 8^{n + 1} ≡ 8^{n + 2} (\\text{mod } 11)$. 8 se naziva prirodni koren Fibonaccijevog broja za 11.</p>\n<p>Nije svaki prost broj sa Fibonaccijevim korenom. Postoji 323 prostih broja ispod 10000 koji imaju jedan ili više Fibonaccijevih korena, a ukupan broj ovih prostih brojeva je 1.480.491.</p>\n<p>Pronađi zbir prim brojeva ispod $100\\,000\\,000$ koji imaju barem jedan Fibonacci broj.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f5241000cf542c510036","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302108,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-437-fibonacci-primitive-roots"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function fibonacciPrimitiveRoots() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nfibonacciPrimitiveRoots();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>fibonacciPrimitiveRoots()</code> bi trebalo da vrati <code>74204709657207</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(fibonacciPrimitiveRoots(), 74204709657207);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-401-to-480","dashedName":"problem-437-fibonacci-primitive-roots","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-438-integer-part-of-polynomial-equations-solutions","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-436-unfair-wager","id":"5900f5241000cf542c510036","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-437-fibonacci-primitive-roots"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}